  "name": "Resist Elements",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The target becomes suffuse with protective magical energies providing some measure of protection against one element: acid, cold/ice, heat/fire, electricity/lightning or sonic/air. The dweomer grants a +2 saving throw bonus against the specified energy type, regardless of whether the source of damage is natural or magical. The spell protects the recipient's equipment as well.</p><p><em>Resist elements</em> absorbs only damage: The caster could still suffer unfortunate side effects. <em>Resist elements</em> overlaps <em>endure elements</em> and <em>protection from elements</em>.</p>",
